headline: Ethan Allen (ETD) Lags Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Ethan Allen (ETD) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.27% and -1.09%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
